M'ara d-uɣalen si ssuq, ad beddlen tikli, ḥesben-t iman-nsent d imhenni, ḥemmlen ad selmen fell-asen.
Di tmurt n Masidunya qṛib a d-kkren ɣer tmurt n Asya d wid yeznuzun itbiren. Di tejmaɛt n Syadi daɣen ilaq ad sɛunt lḥeṛma d leqdeṛ, ad ilin di temdinin n Jlili.
Yella yiwen wergaz ger lmuqedmin imeqqranen n usqamu n ccṛeɛ, isem-is Akilas, laṣel-is n tmurt n Sbanya, ma d wid yessexdamen igellil akken ilaq.
Sɛut iles aẓidan, imeslayen yesɛan lfayda, iwakken aț-țețțarram awal i leǧnas nniḍen ur nelli ara n wat Isṛail.
Seg wasmi i d-texleq ddunit werǧin nesli s tutlayin ur nețwassen ara, d licaṛa i tutlayin ur nețwassen ara, lameɛna yekka-d s ɣuṛ Ṛebbi, lameɛna yekka-d s ɣuṛ-es i wayeḍ. D annect-agi i gebda, tessebleɛ daɣen s tutlayin nniḍen, seg wid i d-yemmeslayen s tutlayt ur nețwassen ara.
M'ara ɛeddin wussan n twaɣit-nni, a ț-yaf zeddiget, tqeɛɛed ; ma d wid iɛeddan fell-asen ad ccetkin fell-asen.
Lemmer nezzenz leɛṭeṛ-nni, tili yewwi-d ssuma tameqqrant ara nefṛeq i rrif n lbabuṛ akk-d laẓ d wamek ara neqdec ɣef yiman-is.
Iqeddacen n tejmaɛt daɣen ilaq ad sɛun leqdeṛ, ad ilin d irgazen iteṭṭfen deg iḍ, ad xḍun i tissit n ccṛab akk-d rrbeḥ n lexdeɛ.
Ɣef wayagi, xḍut i ussexṛeb, ur tețțut ara daɣen belli ilaq-awen aț-țeṭṭfeḍ deg waman-agi deg wemṛaḥ n tẓurin.
